desc: Tidi-Cable's range of products that help get loose cords off the ground in construction areas, reducing the risk of electrocution from cords that are damaged and the risk of slips trips and falls to staff. Helps maintain good housekeeping on projects and comply with OSHA Regulation Standard Number 1926.416.
